## 🏗️ Data Warehouse Architecture

This project follows the **Medallion Architecture (Bronze → Silver → Gold)** to build a structured and scalable data warehouse.

---

### 🥉 Bronze Layer (Raw Data)

* Stores data exactly as received from source systems (CRM & ERP)
* No transformations are applied
* Acts as the **single source of truth**

---

### 🥈 Silver Layer (Cleaned Data)

* Data is cleaned, standardized, and validated
* Handles nulls, formatting issues, and inconsistencies
* Prepares data for further transformation

---

### 🥇 Gold Layer (Business-Ready Data)

* Data is transformed into **analytics-ready datasets**
* Built using **dimension and fact tables (star schema)**
* Contains business logic and integrated data

---

### 🎯 Overall Flow

```text
Raw Data → Cleaned Data → Business Insights
(Bronze)   (Silver)        (Gold)
```

This layered approach improves **data quality, maintainability, and performance**, making it easier to perform analytics and generate insights.
